### 8.2 Performance Optimizations

**Operation Batching:**
```go
type OperationBatcher struct {
    operations []Operation
    timer      *time.Timer
    mu         sync.Mutex
}

func (b *OperationBatcher) AddOperation(op Operation) {
    b.mu.Lock()
    defer b.mu.Unlock()

    b.operations = append(b.operations, op)

    // Batch operations for 10ms or until 100 operations
    if len(b.operations) >= 100 {
        b.flush()
    } else if b.timer == nil {
        b.timer = time.AfterFunc(10*time.Millisecond, b.flush)
    }
}

